    "Title": "Defend Location Against Minor Threats",
    "Description": "ABOUT THE JOB\nmicroTech Protection Services is looking for a detail-oriented mercenary professional who can assemble a security team in order to protect ~mission(Location|Address) against any minor threats. \n\nRESPONSIBILITIES\n\u2022 Provide own transportation to ~mission(Location|Address).\n\u2022 Provide own security team to assist.\n\u2022 Protect the site against hostile threats; using force as necessary.\n\nMINIMUM QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 2 years of combined mercenary and/or security experience.\n\u2022 Access to combat equipment and mode of transport.\n\u2022 Available for immediate deployment.\n\nPREFERRED QUALIFICATIONS\n\u2022 Experience with managing a team.",
